<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 5. Streblocera (Eutanycerus) cornis Chen and van Achterberg, 1997, ♀ A habitus, lateral aspect B first to seventh flagellomeres." , "Figure 8. Streblocera (Eutanycerus) laterostriata Li, Chen and van Achterberg, sp. nov., ♀ F mesosoma, lateral aspect G propodeum, dorsal aspect H first metasomal tergites, dorsal aspect I wings." , "Figure 11. Streblocera (Eutanycerus) opima Chou, 1990, ♀ A habitus, lateral aspect B first to seventh flagellomeres." , "Figure 9. Streblocera (Eutanycerus) lienhuachihensis Chou, 1990, ♀ A habitus, lateral aspect B scapus C first to seventh flagellomeres." , "Figure 20. Streblocera (Streblocera) spasskensis Belokobylskij, 2000, ♀ A habitus, lateral aspcet B scapus." , "Figure 17. Streblocera (Streblocera) interrupta Li, Chen and van Achterberg, sp. nov., ♀ A habitus, lateral aspect B antenna C head, dorsal aspect D head, anterior aspect." , "Figure 7. Streblocera (Eutanycerus) laterostriata Li, Chen and van Achterberg, sp. nov., ♀ A habitus, lateral aspect B ovipositor and its sheaths, lateral aspect C antenna D head, dorsal aspect E head, anterior aspect." , "Figure 14. Streblocera (Eutanycerus) uncifera Li, Chen and van Achterberg, sp. nov., ♀ A abitus, lateral aspect B ovipositor and its sheaths, lateral aspect C scapus D first to seventh flagellomeres, lateral aspect E eighth to twenty-first flagellomeres, lateral aspect F head, dorsal aspect G head, anterior aspect." , "Figure 15. Streblocera (Eutanycerus) uncifera Li, Chen and van Achterberg, sp. nov., ♀ H mesosoma, dorsal aspect I mesosoma, lateral aspect J propodeum, dorsal aspect K first metasomal tergites, dorsal aspect L fore wing." , "Figure 16. Streblocera (Streblocera) emarginata Chou, 1990, ♀, habitus, lateral aspcet." , "Figure 1. Streblocera (Cosmophoridia) flaviceps Marshall, 1898, ♀ A habitus, lateral aspect B antenna C head, anterior aspect." , "Figure 10. Streblocera (Eutanycerus) okadai Watanabe, 1942, ♀ A habitus, lateral aspect B scapus C first to seventh flagellomeres." , "Figure 18. Streblocera (Streblocera) interrupta Li, Chen and van Achterberg, sp. nov., ♀ E mesosoma, dorsal aspect F mesosoma, lateral aspect G propodeum, dorsal aspect H first metasomal tergites, dorsal aspect I fore wing." , "Figure 13. Streblocera (Eutanycerus) tsuifengensis Chou, 1990, ♀ A habitus, lateral aspect B scapus C first to seventh flagellomeres." , "Figure 6. Streblocera (Eutanycerus) hsiufui You, 1999, ♀ A habitus, lateral aspect B first to seventh flagellomeres." , "Figure 21. Streblocera (Streblocera) stigenbergae Li, Chen and van Achterberg, sp. nov., ♀ A habitus, lateral aspect B ovipositor and its sheaths, lateral aspect C antenna D first to second flagellomeres, lateral aspect." , "Figure 2. Streblocera (Eutanycerus) carinifera Li, Chen and van Achterberg, sp. nov., ♀ A habitus, lateral aspect B ovipositor and its sheaths, lateral aspect C scapus D flagellomeres, lateral view E head, dorsal aspect F head, anterior aspect." , "Figure 19. Streblocera (Streblocera) jezoensis Belokobylskij, 2000, ♀, habitus, lateral aspcet." , "Figure 3. Streblocera (Eutanycerus) carinifera Li, Chen and van Achterberg, sp. nov., ♀ G mesosoma, dorsal aspect H mesosoma, lateral aspect I propodeum, dorsal aspect J first metasomal tergites, dorsal aspect K fore wing." , "Figure 12. Streblocera (Eutanycerus) sungkangensis Chou, 1990, ♀ A habitus, lateral aspect B scapus C first to seventh flagellomeres." , "Figure 4. Streblocera (Eutanycerus) chaoi You, 1999, ♀ A habitus, lateral aspect B antenna." ;
